        "text": "# Adapt\n\nOpen communication during the Adapt stage is critical and should be communication by engagement and action. Use Commanders Intent over direct orders or what to do.\n\n# Leadership activity\n\n* Craft the conceptual Scaffolding\n* Centralised coherence (understanding) of the big picture and set Vector measures.\n* Design Crews - Using the Briefs, Goals and Missions design, set the reporting cadence.\n* Design and make Social Network Stimulation interventions - de-risk these through using informal networks and enable spontaneity and awareness across Crews.\n* Co-ordinate portfolio of interventions using the approach designed in Assess stage, weave together insights from the Crews.\n"
