        "text": "# Tasks and activities\n\n* Work at a coherent level of granularity - generally this means at a lower, or more finely grained level.\n* Break up consensus, reduce team sizes, set up Crews.\n* Fragment information to increase knowledge transfer and creation, as well as increase the options to recombine and repurpose later.\nReduce the cadence, focus on Weak Signals identified from the Human Sensor Network, monitor for anything that appears to be stabilising.\n* Map and manage dispositions. Focus on how to create 'more stories like this, less like that'\nDispositional Exaptation or Adjacent Possibles - monitor for opportunities and issues.\n* Continuous mapping and managing of constraints and boundaries.\n"
